@startuml
left to right direction

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

legend bottom
|= Color |= Meaning |
|<#FFCC99>| Corrected existing element |
|<#C6EFCE>| Newly added element |
endlegend

[Client]
note left: Mobile app

package EdgeCluster {
    [LoadBalancer]#C6EFCE
    [Gateway]#FFCC99
    note right
    - Auth
    - Rate limiter
    - HTTP API routing
    - WebSocket upgrade
    end note
}

package UserServiceCluster {
    [UserService] #FFCC99
}

package RealtimeCluster {
    [LocationService] #FFCC99
    [PresenceService] #C6EFCE
}

database UserStorage #FFCC99
note right of UserStorage
PostgreSQL
- users
- canonical friendships
- privacy settings
- block list
end note

database FriendGraphCache #C6EFCE
note right of FriendGraphCache
Redis cache
- confirmed friends only
- hot-path friend reads
end note

database ActiveLocationStore #C6EFCE
note right of ActiveLocationStore
Redis GEO + TTL
- latest location per user
- active presence window
end note

database LocationHistoryStorage #FFCC99
note right of LocationHistoryStorage
Cassandra
- append-only history
- time-bucketed partitions
end note

queue LiveUpdateBus #C6EFCE {
    queue NearbyLocationEvents
}
note right of LiveUpdateBus
Best-effort Pub/Sub
- not source of truth
- latest-state notifications only
end note

[Client] <---> [LoadBalancer]
[LoadBalancer] <---> [Gateway]

[Gateway] <--> [UserService] : HTTPS\nmanage users and friendships
[UserService] <--> UserStorage : read/write users, friendships, privacy
[UserService] --> FriendGraphCache : refresh confirmed-friend cache

[Gateway] <--> [PresenceService] : WebSocket session lifecycle
note on link
- Connect / reconnect
- Heartbeat
- Session registration
- Targeted push to active clients
end note

[Gateway] <--> [LocationService] : HTTPS / WebSocket\nlocation updates
note on link
- Update location
  > latitude, longitude, accuracy
- Fetch nearby active friends
  < latest visible friend locations
end note

[LocationService] <.. FriendGraphCache : get confirmed friends
[LocationService] --> ActiveLocationStore : upsert latest location + TTL
[LocationService] --> LocationHistoryStorage : append sampled history
[LocationService] --> LiveUpdateBus : publish latest-state change

[PresenceService] <.. ActiveLocationStore : query nearby active friends
[PresenceService] <.. LiveUpdateBus : consume best-effort updates
[PresenceService] --> Gateway : push visible friend updates

@enduml
